                    <listitem>
                        <para>&#x2610; Every day</para>
                    </listitem>
                    <listitem>
                        <para>&#x2610; Some days</para>
                    </listitem>
                    <listitem>
                        <para>&#x2610; Not at all</para>
                    </listitem>
                </itemizedlist></para>
            <para>[Section Prompt: Have you ever used tobacco?]</para>
            <para>[Technical Note: Display the following only if current tobacco use is “not at all”.]</para>
            <para><itemizedlist mark="none">
                    <listitem>
                        <para>&#x2610; Yes</para>
                    </listitem>
                    <listitem>
                        <para>&#x2610; No</para>
                    </listitem>
                </itemizedlist></para>
            <para>[Section Prompt: Daily alcohol use/Alcoholism?]</para>
